笑傲江湖游戏的命令分为下列几类：

［玩家命令］

alias	desc	finger	help	hp	id	inventory
nick	passwd	quit	save	score	set	suicide
time	unset	uptime	version	who	wimpy	wizlist

［探险命令］

ask	buy	close	drop	emote	fight	follow
get	give	go	halt	kill	look	open
put	remove	reply	say	semote	shout	steal
tell	tune	unwield	wear	whisper	wield	sleep
beg

［武功命令］

abadon(fangqi)	apprentice(bai)	enable(jifa)	enforce(jiali)
exercise(dazuo)	exert(yun)	expell(kaichu)	learn(xue)	
meditate(tuna)	perform(yong)	practice(lian)	recruit(shou)
skills(cha)	study(du)	prepare(bei)

［巫师命令］

请参照 help wizcmds

